listings.description:
This amazing house is located in Volme, a quiet tourist village ten minutes drive from the Kamenjak National Park. It is equipped with modern high quality furniture. and large terrace is ideal for outdoor dining. Nearest beach is just 3 min away!

House consists of a large patio area for outdoor dining, spacious living room with a sofa bed and kitchen, upstairs there are two double bed bedrooms with terrace and bathroom.
With place being new, modern and fully equipped the only thing left is to relax and have an amazing vacation. :)

Guests have full access to the entire apartment, large terrace and a free private parking space.

We welcome our guests for their stay, offer transport to and from the airport, and are available for contact at any time of the day. :)

Nearest beach is just 3 minutes away on foot and it's pebble. In National Park Kamenjak that is 10 min away with car you can find countless beaches, sandy and pebble.
